Value.CultureInvariantString: The truck driver can drive through strategic zones with the truck - breaking fences, or smashing weak sections of walls to expose alternate entries.
The Noisemaker is a debillitating device that reduces the morale of all who stand in its path. The Noisemaker can be controlled via tablet.
The Ventillation Expert deploys a constant fog of CS gas through specific vents.
The Spotter will report any suspects or civilians that cross its threshold.
The Marksman will report any suspects or civilians that cross its threshold, and can employ a low-power rifle to defuse dicey situations.
The Sniper will report any suspects or civilians that cross its threshold, and can employ a high-power rifle to defuse dicey situations.
Floodlights are a psychological element - allowing a slightly easier time for suspects to surrender, but more importantly, they illuminate darkened areas.
Power crews can cut the power to the establishment, creating a dim environment that makes it difficult for suspects to see you.
The Hostage Negotiator will reduce the number of hostages that appear by offering cash, food, or other items to the suspects in exchange for the hostages.
